		14) More Looting
		15) Delainy and Lahl
		16) Beasts of Balduran's Isle
		17) Palin's Monsters
		18) Murdering Meym
		19) The Sirine Queen
		20) Don't Kryla Wolf
		21) Dradeel
		22) Balduran's Ship, First Level
		23) Balduran's Ship, Second Level
		24) Balduran's Ship, Third Level
		25) Showdown with Karoug
